        <h2>Solar Panel Recycling Guide</h2>
        
        <h3 style="color: #4a7c2c; margin-top: 2rem;">What to Do When Your Panel Expires</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Stop using the panel immediately after expiry</li>
            <li>Contact an authorized recycler from our directory</li>
            <li>Schedule a pickup or drop-off</li>
            <li>Get a recycling certificate</li>
        </ol>

        <h3 style="color: #4a7c2c; margin-top: 2rem;">Safe Storage Steps</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Store panels in a dry, covered area</li>
            <li>Keep away from direct sunlight and moisture</li>
            <li>Stack panels carefully to prevent breakage</li>
            <li>Label panels as "End of Life - For Recycling"</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="color: #4a7c2c; margin-top: 2rem;">Do's and Don'ts</h3>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
            <div>
                <h4 style="color: #28a745;">✓ Do's</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Contact certified recyclers</li>
                    <li>Keep installation records</li>
                    <li>Handle with care</li>
                    <li>Follow local regulations</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 style="color: #dc3545;">✗ Don'ts</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Don't throw in regular trash</li>
                    <li>Don't break or dismantle panels</li>
                    <li>Don't burn or bury panels</li>
                    <li>Don't ignore expiry dates</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3 style="color: #4a7c2c; margin-top: 2rem;">Recycling Process</h3>
        <p>Modern solar panel recycling can recover:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>95% of glass</strong> - Used in new panels or construction</li>
            <li><strong>85% of silicon</strong> - Reused in electronics</li>
            <li><strong>100% of metals</strong> - Aluminum, copper, silver</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="color: #4a7c2c; margin-top: 2rem;">Environmental Benefits</h3>
        <p>Proper recycling prevents toxic materials from entering landfills and reduces the need for mining new materials, contributing to a circular economy.</p>
